msgid "装饰器用法"
msgstr "装饰器用法"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:25
msgid "基本语法"
msgstr "基本语法"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:43
msgid "提示：函数体不会被执行，DocString 才是 Prompt；建议直接使用 `pass`。"
msgstr ""
"Tip: The function body will not be executed, DocString is the Prompt; it is "
"recommended to directly use `pass`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:45
msgid "参数说明"
msgstr "参数说明"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:47
msgid "**llm_interface** (必需): LLM 接口实例，用于与大语言模型通信"
msgstr "**llm_interface** (必需): LLM 接口实例，用于与大语言模型通信"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:48
msgid "**toolkit** (可选): 工具列表，可以是 Tool 对象或被 @tool 装饰的函数"
msgstr "**toolkit** (可选): 工具列表，可以是 Tool 对象或被 @tool 装饰的函数"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:49
msgid "**max_tool_calls** (可选): 最大工具调用次数，防止无限循环，默认为 5"
msgstr "**max_tool_calls** (可选): 最大工具调用次数，防止无限循环，默认为 5"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:50
msgid "**system_prompt_template** (可选): 自定义系统提示模板"
msgstr "**system_prompt_template** (可选): 自定义系统提示模板"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:51
msgid "**user_prompt_template** (可选): 自定义用户提示模板"
msgstr "**user_prompt_template** (可选): 自定义用户提示模板"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:52
msgid "**enable_event** (可选): 是否启用事件流，默认为 False"
msgstr ""
"enable_event (optional): Whether to enable event streaming, default is False"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:53
msgid "`False`: 正常执行，直接返回解析后的结果（向后兼容模式）"
msgstr ""
"True: Normal execution, directly return the parsed result (backward "
"compatibility mode)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:54
msgid "`True`: 返回一个异步生成器，yield `ReactOutput`（`ResponseYield` 或 `EventYield`）"
msgstr ""
"`True`: Returns an asynchronous generator that yields `ReactOutput` "
"(`ResponseYield` or `EventYield`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:55
msgid "详细说明请参考 [事件流系统文档](event_stream.md)"
msgstr ""
"For detailed explanation, please refer to the [Event Stream "
"Documentation](event_stream.md)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:56
msgid ""
"****llm_kwargs**: 额外的关键字参数，将直接传递给 LLM 接口（如 temperature、top_p 等）；可传入 "
"`retry_times` 控制空响应重试次数（默认 2）"
msgstr ""
"**llm_kwargs**: Additional keyword parameters that will be passed directly "
"to the LLM interface (such as temperature, top_p, etc.); you can pass "
"`retry_times` to control the number of retries for empty responses (default "
"2)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:58
msgid "运行时中断（AbortSignal）"
msgstr "Runtime Abort (AbortSignal)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:60
msgid ""
"通过 `_abort_signal` 传入 `AbortSignal`，可在运行中中断当前回合（停止流式输出并取消正在执行的工具调用）。 当 "
"`enable_event=True` 时可以用 `async for` 消费输出并随时触发中断；非事件流模式也可传入 `_abort_signal` "
"来提前终止 `await`。"
msgstr ""
"Pass an `AbortSignal` through `_abort_signal` to interrupt the current turn "
"during execution (stop streaming output and cancel the tool call being "
"executed). When `enable_event=True`, you can use `async for` to consume "
"output and trigger interruption at any time; in non-event streaming mode, "
"you can also pass `_abort_signal` to terminate `await` early."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/llm_function.md:86
msgid ""
"当 `enable_event=True` 时，`ReactEndEvent.extra` 会包含 `aborted: true` 和可选的 "
"`abort_reason`。 详见 [中断与取消](abort.md)。"
msgstr ""
"When `enable_event=True`, `ReactEndEvent.extra` contains `aborted: true` and"
" optional `abort_reason`. See [Interruption and Cancellation](abort.md)."

